<br>
Well, to me, it would be neat if camping out in an inn or a building like an inn would (after an hour of real life time) result in your character logging in with full mana and health (while perhaps preserving buffs / removing curses or DoTs--or just keeping the buffs/dots the same but full health mana).  <br>
<br>
Just a small feature that would bring people back to cities and add a small roleplaying / fun part back to the game. As long as you had to be out of game for a RL hour or more I don't really see this being an exploitable either.<br>
<br>
Any thoughts?<br>
<br>
Kimmy<br>
