<br>
I dont understand the point, either, of having inns in the Commons or in the cities if you cant actually &quot;rest&quot; in them. Kinda pointless.<br>
<br>
<br>
I think all spells, positive or negative, should wear off and you should regain mana and health. Its not possible to exploit it if you camp out for a hour RL time. <br>
<br>
Course, I had an odd &quot;bug&quot; happen when I first started playing Zaith. I would be almost dead and with zero mana and decide to camp out, anyplace in the game mind you. I would come back, either the next day or an hour later, and find myself at full health and mana. I really didnt understand why it happend and normaly I wouldnt remember if I had full health/mana when I camped anyway, but after almost dying to a few wisps in the commons, I camped to go eat or something. came back a hourish later and found full health/mana. <br>
<br>
